quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,62,"yeh log tumahray samnay kasmain khatay hain taakay tumhe raazi karen, halaank agar yeh momin hain to Allah aur rasool is ke ziyada haq daar hain ke yeh un ko raazi karne ki fikar karen"
9,63,kya inhen maloom nahi hai ke jo Allah aur is ke rasool ka muqaabla karta hai is ke liye dozakh ki aag hai jis mein woh hamesha rahay ga yeh bohat barri ruswai hai
9,64,"yeh munafiq dar rahay hain ke kahin musalmanoon par koi aisi sourat nazil nah ho jaye jo un ke dilon ke bhaid khol kar rakh day ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho,"" aur mazaq urrao, Allah uss cheez ko khol dainay wala hai jis ke khil jaane se tum drtay ho """
9,65,"agar un se pucho ke tum kya baatein kar rahay thay, to jhat keh den ge ke hum to hansi mazaq aur dil lagi kar rahay thay un se kaho,"" kya tumhari hansi dil lagi Allah aur uss ki ayaat aur is ke rasool hi ke sath thi ?"
9,66,"ab uzraat nahtrasho tum ne imaan laane ke baad kufar kya hai, agar hum ne tum mein se aik giroh ko maaf kar bhi diya to dosray giroh ko to hum zaroor saza den ge kyunkay woh mujrim hai """
9,67,munafiq mard aur munafiq aurtain sab aik dosray ke hum rang hain buraiee ka hukum dete hain aur bhalai se mana karte hain aur apne haath kher se rokay rakhtay hain yeh Allah ko bhool gay to Allah ne bhi inhen bhala diya yaqeenan yeh munafiq hi fasik hain
9,68,"un munafiq mardon aur aurton aur kafiroon ke liye Allah ne aatish dozakh ka wada kya hai jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge, wohi un ke liye mozoon hai un par Allah ki phatkaar hai aur un ke liye qaim rehnaywala azaab hai"
